result.title: Relative popularity of MLP
result.description:
Relative popularity of My Little Pony over time. That is, average score (solid) and fav count(dashed) as compared to the average of all submissions. Compare to Google search trends:

<script type="text/javascript" src="https://ssl.gstatic.com/trends_nrtr/1671_RC04/embed_loader.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    trends.embed.renderExploreWidget("TIMESERIES", {"comparisonItem":[{"keyword":"my little pony","geo":"US","time":"2007-02-10 2018-12-17"}],"category":0,"property":""}, {"exploreQuery":"date=2007-02-10%202018-12-17&geo=US&q=my%20little%20pony","guestPath":"https://trends.google.com:443/trends/embed/"});
</script>

The spike in September/October 2017 is when the MLP movie came out in theaters.
result.runner_help_text:
### Relative tag popularity over month.

This runner gets the popularity of a given tag in relation to the
popularity of all posts broken down by month.

Attributes:

* `tag` - the tag to search for.
